<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Password on Aurora</title><link>https://notes.yoooo.fun/tags/password/</link><description>Recent content in Password on Aurora</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 10:42:36 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://notes.yoooo.fun/tags/password/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Quick Start: SSP</title><link>https://notes.yoooo.fun/posts/quick-start-6-ldap-ssp/</link><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jul 2023 15:20:21 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://notes.yoooo.fun/posts/quick-start-6-ldap-ssp/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="quick-start-ssp"&gt;Quick Start: SSP
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;SSP(&lt;code&gt;Self-Service Password&lt;/code&gt;), is a tool for ldap to change password.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="prerequisite"&gt;Prerequisite
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://blog.yoooo.fun/quick-start-1-traefik.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Traefik on HTTP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;OR&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://blog.yoooo.fun/quick-start-1-1-traefik-ssl.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;Traefik on HTTPS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note: If using HTTP, remove the &lt;code&gt;tls: {}&lt;/code&gt; in dynamic configuration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="https://blog.yoooo.fun/quick-start-2_1-bitnami-ldap.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
&gt;LDAP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
